content: Enjoy the music. How ever disappointed to learn after paying for the NO ADS version that the music still stops playing every 15-20 minutes. Annoying and frustrating to have to restart it all the time not to mention the disruption breaking up the mental relaxation.
Best
Love this app especially the saxaphone. I am looking on Apple as well but can't find it. Help??

I love how it calms, focuses the brain & brings mindfullness into my daily routine. Of course I loved having no adds. The downside is there no settings in which you could make in the main menu to be to apply to the whole app in general. Though I was expecting Relaxing Music 2021 w added music, meditations & features plus no adds, I will continue using both apps because I do love how they heal the body mind & soul. I just wish that it was all in one app to save space on my devices.
Great for relaxing and reading.

Love this app worth paying for. I use it every night. I am now disappointed with the app ever since I paid for it it continues to stop when playing. Before it never did. Become more disappointed every day since paying for app as it cuts out .
I love this. It is comprehensive and the music and meditations are well done
Have always enjoyed using this app until recently. Music has been stopping at around 20 minutes. I use this at work and all night. I need it to continue to play. Please fix this.
Fault app stops on every track at the 30minutes and closes the app from continue playing with the button that controls the flow of music.
When it was free worked fine. I paid for it and it continuously stops... Please fix this Thanks
Good selection

It's a good app, but it'd be good if we had the ability to download songs, because buffering takes too long. Also adding favourites would be nice, so we don't need to always search for favourite sounds.
I love the app, and use it every day but the long items seem to have stopped working, which is disappointing. I love the variety of options and would love to keep some going for the indicated time.
Great selection, it's just a shame that the music cuts out after 15mins. I have to constantly press play and try to remember where I was.

Pros: Great selection of audios! Friendly interface. Wide selections. Cons: Will not work offline. Stop after a while when turn off the screen. Unable to create favorites. Would love to have an offline version and the ability to set timer.
Great music but the app only plays about first 15 minutes of a song and switches to next one
Essential One
Engulfing
Very wonderful app for great relaxation. I love it
Better than others, please include timer mode, and please include Indian Flute and Vedic music as well :)
Please add a sleep timer so it will turn off after setting a time
On call app get paused and after call it is not resuming to play. Musics are good and can be relaxed.
I love the different types of music you have. You have one for every mood, and I was happy to pay that small amount to remove the ads.
Excellent app,. Loads of music options and worth paying the small price to have the no ad version. Went to bed the other night at 9pm, left it playing and woke up at 5am and it was still going.
I love this! There is something for every part of your day and then you can go to the sleep stage üòç
Really good nice melodies and tunes rather than just sounds. Would be even better though if there was a sleep timer and if you could favourite the tunes you like most.
Beautiful Sounds
